{"id":1125,"category_slug":"toeic","category_name":"TOEIC Listening","position":87,"title":"Conversation 47","subtitle":"Air Purifier Troubleshooting Call","level":"B1","parts":19,"url":"https://dailydictation.com/exercises/toeic/conversation-47.1125/listen-and-type","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-47-2023-09-15-20-39-18/0-conversation-47.mp3","transcript":"Dreamer Home Appliances.\nThis is Leonard speaking.\nHow can I help you?\nOh, hi.\nI bought a Philis Brand air purifier from you.\nThe model number is AP1105.\nThe control panel is unresponsive.\nI tried unplugging the power cord and plugging it back in,\nbut it just won't power on.\nDon't worry, let's figure it out.\nUmm... First, insert the filters in the air purifier housing,\nand then replace the front grille.\nNote that you should fix it in place by twisting it.\nNext, press and hold the reset button for 5 seconds\nto reset the filter lifetime counter.\nOh, it worked!\nI can't believe I missed the last step.\nI should've read the manual in the first place.\nThanks so much.","youtube_video_id":"","details_cached_at":"2026-06-15T21:00:18","challenges":[{"position":1,"content":"Dreamer Home Appliances.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-47-2023-09-15-20-39-18/1.mp3","time_start":0.37,"time_end":2.42},{"position":2,"content":"This is Leonard speaking.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-47-2023-09-15-20-39-18/2.mp3","time_start":2.42,"time_end":4.32},{"position":3,"content":"How can I help you?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-47-2023-09-15-20-39-18/3.mp3","time_start":4.32,"time_end":5.74},{"position":4,"content":"Oh, hi.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-47-2023-09-15-20-39-18/4.mp3","time_start":5.74,"time_end":6.94},{"position":5,"content":"I bought a Philis Brand air purifier from you.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/convers